#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
AgoraIQ — Telegram Channel Listener

Monitors configured Telegram channels for trading signals,
parses them with regex + LLM fallback, and POSTs to the
AgoraIQ ingestion API.

Usage:
  First run (interactive):  python3 listener.py
    → Prompts for phone number + 2FA code to create session
  
  Daemon mode (after session created):
    pm2 start listener.py --interpreter python3 --name agoraiq-listener

Environment:
  TG_API_ID, TG_API_HASH     — from my.telegram.org
  TG_SESSION_NAME             — session file name (default: agoraiq_listener)
  AGORAIQ_API_URL             — ingestion base URL
  LISTENER_LOG_LEVEL          — DEBUG/INFO/WARNING (default: INFO)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
"""

